Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:06.31,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Barley tea, roasted green tea, roasted rice tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:10.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of teas, \Nbut is there a wheat tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:13.53,Main - Top,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-kun was famous for not \Nletting anyone into her room...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.55,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Practically famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:21.52,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,I thought Tsukasa-kun's \Ntrue love was Kokona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.83,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,This is a surprising development, yo yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:30.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's so big! Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:33.41,Main - Top,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,W-Wait! It's not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.23,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,It's big...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:36.50,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so nice and soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.18,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,It's soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.16,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,What are you girls doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.43,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Nothing, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:44.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I had no idea they made \Nsuch big marshmallows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.41,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I want to eat them right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:49.02,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Everything's ready. It's happy tea time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:49.98,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:54.65,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Kokona sure is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:57.41,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Those clothes look really \Ngood on you, Tsukasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.49,Main,TSUKSA,0,0,0,,R-Really? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I think you'd be popular as \Nlovely Tsukasa-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.49,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:07.60,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I thought about coming out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:11.49,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,but I think I'm successful as an idol \Nbecause of my masculine character.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:13.23,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:14.38,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:18.69,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Kokona-san, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:21.80,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Next up are "Sumo Puri" and "The Kunoichis."
