Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.32,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,You seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:14.29,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah, I couldn't sleep because of \Neverything that happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.59,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,"Everything"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,We were having fun talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but then a nuisance suddenly showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.02,Main - Flashback,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,{\a6}Pyon, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.26,Main - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Pyon, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.68,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.22,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,So we were up late fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.32,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but ultimately I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.06,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,They were having fun talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.40,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,When a nuisance suddenly appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.37,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,And Komugi-chan won the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.15,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Seriously, yo yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That's why I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.57,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,That really happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.25,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Good navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, Kokona-chan, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.37,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,G-Good navel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.71,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,You seem kind of different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.97,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Y-You think so, navel? I'm my usual self, navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.23,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Did you cut your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.21,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,No, I didn't, navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.19,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Did you lose some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.98,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Of course not, navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.35,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh! Your navel's showing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.12,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.40,Main,TAMAKO,0,0,0,,N-A-V-E-L, navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.19,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Y-You noticed, navel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.39,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about becoming \Na bellybutton idol, navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.95,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,A bellybutton idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.60,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Really? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.79,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I-I don't think I'm good enough as I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.24,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,S-So I thought I'd change my image, navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.56,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,A new image because your heart was broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:42.17,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Is this a case of a pure idol \Nstarting to show more skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.64,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Exposing yourself is the \Ngateway to delinquency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.88,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,You should respect yourself more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.89,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,You're making me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.17,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,It's so heartbreaking, I can't bear to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.44,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Don't be a bellybutton idol. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.86,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I-Is it really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.34,downtown mall,,0,0,0,,Celebrating Saionji Kokona's New Single\N{\c&Hafa46a&\fs18}Handshake & Autograph Event!
