Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.82,downtown mall,,0,0,0,,Handshake\NEvent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.27,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you, 'stache.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.00,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you, 'stache.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.91,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Um, Kokonacchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:17.67,downtown mall,,0,0,0,,Handshake\NEvent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.72,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,That's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.85,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.17,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Would this one be better, mustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:19.94,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Mustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:24.05,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,I-I think you look better without a mustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.67,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.96,Main,MC,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan, you seem \Nawfully different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:37.27,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I-I thought I'd try wearing \Nsomething a little bolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.62,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm Mentaikokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.61,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I brought some friends with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:45.53,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This is Suketo-chan, and \Nthat's Udara-chan, mentai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.11,Main,MC,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.45,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Okay, let's stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.00,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Someone save Udara-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.94,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Saving Udara-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.68,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,She's been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.46,Main,AI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.46,love pro,SIGN,0,0,0,,Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:00.15,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,She's normally so serious. \NI'm worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.53,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Well, it's a confusing time for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.48,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.20,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Let her do what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.09,Main,AI,0,0,0,,If anything happens, \NI'll take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.97,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Kokona will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.54,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Y-You're right! Kokona will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:15.85,brown part of sign,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Guest Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.10,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.48,brown part of sign,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Guest Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.48,white part of sign,,0,0,0,,Saionji\NKokona-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:19.44,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,There must be some persona I haven't tried yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.35,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,She's talking to herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.45,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,If mentaiko isn't working, \Nhow about sea cucumbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.56,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should move \Naway from raw foods, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Poko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.61,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Kokona, is somebody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.91,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Th-There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:37.11,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Really? I thought I heard \Na low voice saying "poko."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.35,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Y-You're just imagining things, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.42,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.42,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You're trying a tanuki persona next!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.13,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.01,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Just do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.25,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You're okay! You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.56,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:50.33,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Po-poko-pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.47,yoshida clinic,,0,0,0,,{\an2}Yoshida Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.22,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Mentaikokonacchi is really cute, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.09,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,I wonder if there'll be any merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.34,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,My, Kokona-chan has changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.24,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,All kinds of rare Kokonacchis \Nhave been coming out lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:08.33,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,What kind of Kokonacchi will we see next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.48,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}Doing Sports{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.53,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm your reporter, Saionji Kokona, nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.93,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Today's special report is on marathons, nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.92,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,First up is an interview with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.42,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Olympic gold medalist Michio Kakeru-san, nyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.86,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:30.65,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Michio-san, you announced \Nyour retirement the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.60,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to retire, nyah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.10,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,My strength has reached its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.55,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I see, nyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:42.34,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Even though you've participated \Nin countless races,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.94,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,you couldn't overcome the \Nwall that is aging, nyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.56,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Why do you keep saying "nyah?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.23,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of marathons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.27,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,It's obnoxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:53.64,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,C-Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.41,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.74,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,You're killing me, Kokona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.91,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.46,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.44,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You're so cool, Tsukasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.18,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:19.34,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.60,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.10,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I don't have any kind of persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.01,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Persona?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.46,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Lately, girls with specific\Npersonas get all the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:33.35,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm worried that, at this rate, \NI won't become Japan's top idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:37.24,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,or even get any work at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:40.01,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Do you want to try crossdressing too, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:40.79,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.01,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It wouldn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.20,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.21,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.34,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:57.15,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I dress like a man because I'm better \Nsuited to it than any other idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.76,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,and it's my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.26,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.74,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,A persona isn't about wishing \Nfor what you can't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.56,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's about developing a certain trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.15,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Developing a certain trait?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.29,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'm heading back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.97,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What traits do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.91,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan, Kokona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.18,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.92,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,There you are! Filming is going to start soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.66,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.79,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,T-Totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.49,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My toughness is my only strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.67,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm the super energetic Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:40.01,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Just watching you fills me with energy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.35,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That's your strength as an idol, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.06,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I don't have anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.34,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.06,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You've got tons of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:50.56,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You're cute, you're good at singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.84,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,you're a super lovely dancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:59.69,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,you're quick to memorize your lines, \Nyou never mess up difficult lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.62,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and you're really good at your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.41,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,There's no end to your strengths!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.91,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But your greatest strength \Nis how hard you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:11.33,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I think you work harder than anybody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:14.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and that's a really wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.92,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, filming is about to start! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.51,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Being hardworking is my persona?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:30.31,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:35.13,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry for upsetting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.61,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,No, I was childish, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.93,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to take this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.90,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,After all, marathons are my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:42.83,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.75,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Next, could you tell us what you \Nfind appealing about marathons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:52.54,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Well, I like how they're a \Nbattle against yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.59,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Marathons are very strenuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.66,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,but by working hard to overcome that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.75,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,you feel as though you're really alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:02.21,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I can see that marathons are very profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:06.60,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,For those of you who feel inspired \Nto run a marathon after hearing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.06,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,here's an announcement about \Nthe Shitamachi Marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.42,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:14.40,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'm Shitamachi Marathon \Nsupporter Kisaragi Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.40,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And I'm Marathonne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:20.61,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The Shitamachi Marathon is a local marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.62,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Anyone who's confident in their \Nphysical abilities can participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.30,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The carefree quality of public marathons \Nis one reason they're popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.08,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Now it's time for a commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.46,Main - Flashback,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,A persona isn't about wishing \Nfor what you can't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.27,Main - Flashback,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's about developing a certain trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.69,Main - Flashback,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But your greatest strength \Nis how hard you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.98,marathon,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shitamachi Marathon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.66,love pro,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an1}Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:02.66,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,President Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.12,Main,AI,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I want to participate in \Nthe Shitamachi Marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.72,Main,AI,0,0,0,,What? A marathon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.66,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:16.18,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I was concerned that I didn't have a persona,\Nbut nothing I did seemed to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.76,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,But I realized the only thing I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.84,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,is do my very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.33,Main,AI,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.30,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,By doing my best to complete a marathon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.94,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I believe I'll be able to face my own persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.73,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.23,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:41.15,takes on a marathon,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an8}Saionji Kokona \N{\c&Hffab92&}attempts a full \Nmarathon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.32,Main,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Saionji Kokona-san will attempt \Nto complete a full marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.15,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.05,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Kokonacchi's running in \Nthe Shitamachi Marathon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.28,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,I have to support her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.70,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,Attempting a Full Marathon! \NIdol from Kyushu \NSaionji Kokona-san (14)\N"Trying my hardest is who I am."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.85,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Let's get started, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.43,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.28,you can do it,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\pos(216,144)}You can do it, Kokonacchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:29.61,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.71,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,The skies are clear, making this \Na perfect day for a marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.84,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,The Shitamachi Marathon \Nwill begin momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:48.25,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Here with me as a guest analyst is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:50.77,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Olympic gold medalist Michio Kakeru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:51.85,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:55.14,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Supporter Kisaragi Tsukasa-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.99,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,will be starting the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.65,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.03,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,And they're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.61,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Kokonacchi, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.62,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,What do you think of Kokona's form?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.00,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Her form's so good, I can't believe \Nthis is her first marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.14,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,I hope she can keep up this pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.00,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,We're approaching the midpoint of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.92,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Things will start getting \Nphysically difficult here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.43,you can do it,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs18}Shitamachi \NShopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.83,Main,GOTO,0,0,0,,Good work, Tsukasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.95,Main,GOTO,0,0,0,,You're free until the award ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:36.77,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.19,Main,GOTO,0,0,0,,"Nya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.27,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,N-Nyah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.42,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Something suddenly came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.11,Main,GOTO,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Buri Bara's new \Nseries goes on sale today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.60,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I sense a monster, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.35,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's time to Chan-G, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:50.57,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Stop flailing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.80,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Some participants have slowed to a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:58.04,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,From here on, the race will become difficult \Nnot only physically, but also mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:02.54,Main - Italics,TANUP,0,0,0,,I-I'm sensing a monster now, of all times, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.26,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Leap, youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:12.26,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Leap, something-forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.09,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:15.60,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,His leg strength is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:19.70,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,In any case, nothing beats leaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.53,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Operation: Leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.02,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.67,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:29.65,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,A mysterious girl leaped into the race, and \Nboth she and the monster have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.24,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Such incredible leg strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:36.57,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Oh? Another mysterious girl \Nhas appeared... and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.16,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Such incredible leg strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:41.05,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Fans of funny videos might forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:44.04,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,evildoers who interfere \Nwith marathons, but I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.13,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The Magical Nurse has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.99,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Sister-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.70,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,You got here a little late, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:53.00,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Shut up! We'll see who beats it, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.91,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:55.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.68,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,I can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:58.85,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.94,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Use your Muscle Hustle Bouncy Beam, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.54,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The Muscle Hustle Bouncy Beam is produced
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:17.21,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,when the electric currents released \Nby excited Amazoni-N Cells collide
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:20.98,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,and are discharged in a massive \Nbolt of lightning toward the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.96,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It's a special attack that purifies enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.46,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Nurse Thunder
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.21,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sparkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:41.26,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,"Not-Leaping-Into-Traffic Boy" \Nis a more accurate name
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:44.02,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,than "Leaping-Into-Traffic Boy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.24,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,We got the Fan-C Card, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.67,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,You thieving rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.08,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,I'll skin you and turn you into a scarf, nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.28,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:59.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Here. You're the reason we beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Too bad for you, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.42,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's fine. You're the one who took him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.12,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Can't we beat monsters by working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.06,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.80,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,We've come to the latter half of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.05,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Kokona seems to be having a tough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.03,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.98,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,You seem to be struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.70,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Are you all right, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.58,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's hard... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.91,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,But it's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.74,Main - Top,MICHIO,0,0,0,,As far as I can tell, \Nher legs are past their limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.13,Main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Kokonacchi, I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.56,Main - Top,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Perhaps she's running on willpower alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.99,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,K-Kokonacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.57,Main,BOY,0,0,0,,Mom, Grandpa stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.48,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Why can't you even shake hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.57,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.67,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,I see. She's at the critical moment that \Ndecides whether or not she'll finish the race...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.20,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.03,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,The way she's running is... How can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.28,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,I guess you could call it touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.67,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:49.59,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Michio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.76,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Running this race made me realize something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.06,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I have so many people who support me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.86,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,even when I'm not singing or dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.78,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,H-How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:08.60,Main,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,As if inspired by Kokona, \Nother people have begun running!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.19,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I thought I always had to place first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.61,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I thought I had to become \Nthe best idol in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:17.12,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,Be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.82,Main - Flashback,DAD,0,0,0,,If you're going to do it, \Nyou have to be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.12,Main - Flashback,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.99,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,But things are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.62,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I want to become the idol only I can become.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.12,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I don't need to be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.85,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I want to become an idol \Nwho gives others energy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:34.81,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,and puts a smile on their \Nfaces by working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:37.50,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,You have a wonderful daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.54,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,Do you know why
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.37,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,parents criticize every little \Nthing their children do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:45.10,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,So they'll do their best at \Nwhatever they want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.42,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,despite opposition and criticism \Nfrom their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:49.87,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:50.94,Main,MOM,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.74,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,Her expression is brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.63,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,She doesn't have to be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.94,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,As long as she does her best,\Nthat's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.32,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,That alone makes her the greatest idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.99,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:04.44,Main,DAD,0,0,0,,You can do it, Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:05.74,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.46,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.55,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Kokona! Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.88,Main - Top,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,Kokona, along with a crowd of fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:20.66,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Kokona! Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:23.01,Main - Top,,0,0,0,,has reached the goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:25.31,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Kokonacchi shines the brightest \Nwhen she's doing her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:32.81,Main - Italics,COMMENTATOR,0,0,0,,...has reached the goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.66,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.36,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This feels great after working up such a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.90,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'll wash your back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:40.54,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.32,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,As a reward for finishing the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.13,Main,KOKNA,0,0,0,,I guess I'll take you up on that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.16,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.27,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Now, this is the back of a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.04,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thanks. It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.16,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:58.02,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,No, you and Komugi-chan \Nhelped me realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.94,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have noticed on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.72,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,That was a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.87,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Th-That scared me, darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.89,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I bet you have another persona hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.74,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,under your crossdressing persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.73,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.65,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,N-No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.22,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Of course I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.74,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,There, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.49,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,N-Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:24.01,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's your fault for saying weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.47,dorm mimosa night,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1585)}Nijigaoka Academy Student Dorm Mimosa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:00.15,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}Doing Sports{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.38,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm your reporter, Saionji Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:06.50,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Today's guest is Michio Kakeru,\Nwho suddenly returned to running
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:09.85,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,after his retirement announcement,\Nand went on to win
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:13.56,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,the Tokyo Marathon held immediately after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.87,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,Hello. I thought I had reached my limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:18.63,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,but after seeing you run,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:21.79,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,my passion for running was revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:25.08,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,I always listen to your songs while I train.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:27.03,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:29.17,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:30.87,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,My favorite idol is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:34.08,Main,MICHIO,0,0,0,,over there, over here, Kokonacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:45.34,Next Time,TEXT,0,0,0,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:37.04,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Neko-P comin' at nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:39.71,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,I was wonderin' why women \Nfrom Kansai wear clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:41.46,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,with lion and tiger faces on 'em, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.92,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Apparently it makes them feel speedier, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.34,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from Kansai, nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:47.55,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,The next episode is \N"Yuto's Fruitless Romantic Endeavor."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:50.05,next ep title,TEXT,0,0,0,,Yuto's Fruitless \NRomantic Endeavor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:49.63,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Speaking in Kansai dialect sure is hard, nyan.